				<div style="text-indent:30px; margin-top:-20px">
					<ul>
						<li><a href="./bitbucket_hosting.html">Hosting on BitBucket</a>;</li>
						<li><a href="./github_hosting.html">Hosting on GitHub</a>; or</li>
						<li><a href="./gitlab_hosting.html">Hosting on GitLab</a>.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<p>
					To host dynamic websites for free check out <a href="https://www.heroku.com/">Heroku</a>. Other options for hosting dynamic websites (or static sites if you would like) include hiring a server with somewhere like:
